  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend one superiority die to attempt to disarm the target, forcing it to drop one item of your choice that it's holding. You add the superiority die to the attack's damage roll, and the target must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, it drops the object you choose. The object lands at its feet.</p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">Note: After adding this feature to your character, edit this feature's details and set Resource Consumption to Items Uses: Combat Superiority.</em></p>",
